Preconditions:
- The input parameter `n` must be a positive integer.
- The input parameter `q` must be a 2D array of integers.

Postconditions:
- The returned array `answer` must have the same length as the input array `q`.
- Each element `answer[i]` in the returned array must be an integer representing the number of adjacent elements with the same color after the `i-th` query.